com.ephesoft.dcma.core.common

Enum CurrencyCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CurrencyCode>
      • com.ephesoft.dcma.core.common.CurrencyCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CurrencyCode>

    public enum CurrencyCode
extends java.lang.Enum<CurrencyCode>
    Used to represent the currency codes of different countries. These currency codes are used to extract currency values, represent Double / Long values in their corressponding currency representation.
    Author:
    Ephesoft
